<P>
 A 25-year-old man pleaded not guilty Friday to kidnaping a 12-year-old girl 
from her Lodi home last weekend. 
</P>
<P>
 Steven Reese Cochran appeared in shackles in San Joaquin Superior Court to 
enter pleas to 21 counts that include kidnaping, burglary and sexual battery. 
</P>
