<P>
 Digital to Close Southwest, Mexico Plants: Digital Equipment Corp., in the 
midst of a deep downturn, said it will close two plants in Albuquerque, N.M., 
and Chihuahua, Mexico, and lay off more than 1,000 employees. The Albuquerque 
plant, with about 440 employees, performs assembly, testing and integration of 
