<DOCNO> LA070994-0134 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 058969 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 9, 1994, Saturday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 5; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
