<HEADLINE>
<P>
WEEKEND TV; 'PLAYING FIELD' LEADS THE SUNDAY LINEUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By N. F. MENDOZA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 KNBC-TV Channel 4 will air "The Playing Field," an Emmy-winning baseball 
documentary that goes back to the late 1800s and profiles the players of the 
Negro League, Sunday at 11:30 a.m. N. F. MENDOZA 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA070994-0148 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 058983 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 9, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
