Fanatic? Scapegoat? Half of Italy is gnawing at the clinical and judicial 
'case' of Arrigo Sacchi. . . . (Nothing will) distract the popular tribunal 
made up of 30 million Italians who are summoned tomorrow night to see the 
Italian team win, or the rolling of a bald head with glasses." 
</P>
