</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Brazilians Romario and Bebeto have been getting most of the attention during 
the World Cup tournament, but Swedish forwards Martin Dahlin and Kennet 
Andersson have combined for more goals -- seven.Romario and Bebeto have each 
scored three. 
</P>
<P>
 Dahlin is the son of a Venezuelan musician and a Swedish woman. He grew up in 
Stockholm and says he is a Laker fan. LISA DILLMAN 
</P>
