<P>
 Excessive-force suit -- A Times story Friday on a mistrial in an 
excessive-force lawsuit incorrectly stated that the eight-member jury was split 
5 to 3 in favor of the plaintiffs. The jury actually was split in favor of the 
defendants in the lawsuit, filed by a man who claimed that police overreacted 
when he fired a shotgun blast that wounded two officers. 
